        Import In place, or move/copy. So to import in place use: copyFile=false,importInPlace=true Or to move into atak dir and remove original file use: copyFile=false,importInPlace=false
        Parameters:
        ext -
        folderName -
        validateExt -
        copyFile - true copy, false to move (only used importInPlace=false)
        importInPlace - true to import from source location, false to copy/move into atak data dir
